类 SipConfigManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zhonghu.sip.api.SipConfigManager

  • public class SipConfigManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manage global configuration of the application.
    Provides wrapper around preference content provider and define preference keys constants

      • SND_MEDIA_QUALITY

        public static final java.lang.String SND_MEDIA_QUALITY
        Media quality, 0-10.
        according to this table: 5-10: resampling use large filter
        3-4: resampling use small filter
        1-2: resampling use linear.
        The media quality also sets speex codec quality/complexity to the number.
        Pjsip documentation
        另请参阅:
        setPreferenceIntegerValue(Context, String, Integer), 常量字段值

      • HAS_IO_QUEUE

        public static final java.lang.String HAS_IO_QUEUE
        This option is not used anymore because requires multiple working thread that is not suitable for mobility mode.
        Specify whether the media manager should manage its own ioqueue for the RTP/RTCP sockets.
        If yes, ioqueue will be created and at least one worker thread will be created too.
        If no, the RTP/RTCP sockets will share the same ioqueue as SIP sockets, and no worker thread is needed.
        Pjsip documentation
        另请参阅:
        setPreferenceBooleanValue(Context, String, boolean), 常量字段值

      • getCodecKey

        public static java.lang.String getCodecKey(java.lang.String codecName,
                                           java.lang.String type)
        Get the preference key for a codec priority
        参数:
        codecName - Name of the codec as known by pjsip. Example PCMU/8000/1
        type - Type of the codec CODEC_NB or CODEC_WB
        返回:
        The key to use to set/get the priority of a codec for a given bandwidth

                                              int subType)

        参数:
        networkType - Type of the network ConnectivityManager
        subType - Subtype of the network TelephonyManager
        返回:
        the preference key for the network kind passed in argument
